# read {LICENSE} as RepositoryLicense

The authoritative repository license text.

# res transpilerLicense

An exact package-local copy of {RepositoryLicense}.

# rule

- Preserve the MIT license text verbatim.
- Preserve the copyright line `Copyright (c) 2026 Andrei Neprel`.
- Do not add package-specific exceptions, additional restrictions, or commentary.
- The build metadata staging step must copy this file into the npm artifact.
